reviews.review_text: - The hiss has been removed, but it sounds way too dolbyized for my taste, lacking any high end at all and obviating the need for the recording as a SBD in the first place.

Boo Hoo Dolby It always amazes me how petty-picky Deadheads can be about these recordings.  You're lucky you got anything to listen to let alone a killer SBD like this.  Great show and very nicely cleaned up recording.  Thank you VERY MUCH!
